text: The boxlip mullet (Oedalechilus labeo) is a species of fish in the mullet family which is found in the eastern Atlantic from Gibraltar to Morocco, it is found in the Mediterranean Sea but not the Black Sea. It is the only species in the monospecific genus Oedalechilus. == References == ==External links== * * Category:Mugilidae Category:Fish described in 1829
title: Boxlip mullet
